title: Jay Blades: The Midlands Through Time
overview: In Jay Blades: The Midlands Through Time, Jay travels through Birmingham, Wolverhampton, Coventry and beyond to uncover the fascinating history of an area which has had a profound effect on the development of Great Britain.Jay discovers just how much the nation owes to the West Midlands. Not only is it the home of Wedgwood but it's also the birthplace of the industrial revolution, the home of Wedgwood, the Olympic Games, the theory of Evolution and even the Balti.Â
